surveystatement.name: welcome
surveystatement.statement:
This is part 1 of the survey. The total time to complete both parts is about 20-30 mins. You can take a break after part 1 and continue at a later time for part 2 if needed.
In the survey you will be asked to rate voices, some of the recordings have been generated from AI and others are real.
Thank you for taking the survey and I hope you enjoy it.

interface.name: naturalness
interface.title: Rate each sample how natural it sounds

surveystatement.name: intro_nat_1
surveystatement.statement:
There are 12 pages on this test. On each page there will be 4 or 5 speech samples with a vertical natural rating scale.
1. Click on 'Play' at the bottom of the scale to listen to a speech sample 2. Move the slider to reflect how natural the speech sounds 3. Please listen to each speech sample fully before moving to the next page 4. You do not have to use the full range of the scale if you do not want to 5. Real human speech should be very close to 'Very Natural' and robotic speech would be 'Very Unnatural', but this is a subjective test so use you gut instinct on where the speech samples rate
